. Paratype, ♀ (IEGU), forewing. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[443,464,1987,2013]" pageId="5" pageNumber="69">C</emphasis>
. Paratype, ♀ (IEGU), hind wing. Scale bars: A–C = 0.5 mm. a–e = white parts.
</paragraph>
</caption>
