, paratype, ♂ (IEGU). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1068,1159,1922,1948]" pageId="6" pageNumber="70">A, C, D</emphasis>
. Genitalia in lateral, posterior and ventral view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[510,563,1957,1983]" pageId="6" pageNumber="70">B, E</emphasis>
. Aedeagus, posterior and lateral view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1021,1039,1957,1983]" pageId="6" pageNumber="70">F</emphasis>
. Style, dorsal view. 
